A cyberpunk-style close-up of a sleek, futuristic smartphone hovering above an outstretched hand, bathed in neon pink and electric blue light. The phone's screen glows with an intense teal luminescence, casting dramatic shadows across the palm. Circuit board patterns and holographic data streams float in the air around the device. The background features a rain-slicked urban nightscape with towering buildings adorned with glowing advertisements, all slightly out of focus. Steam rises from street vents below, catching the colorful light. The mood conveys intense technological desire and anticipation, with the phone positioned as an object of obsession.
